data.title: EIPsInsight
data.description: [EIPsInsight](https://eipsinsight.com) is public goods toolings designed to provide clear, visual insights into the activity of [Ethereum Improvement Proposals (EIPs)](https://youtu.be/AyidVR6X6J8), [Ethereum Request for Comments (ERCs)](https://youtu.be/fwxkbUaa92w), and Rollup Improvement Proposals (RIPs). EIPsInsight offers comprehensive tooling to analyze pull requests and provides detailed views of status changes, along with visualizations and downloadable reports for Ethereum Improvement Proposals. This platform supports the Ethereum ecosystem by helping developers and editors navigate and understand the intricacies of these proposals more effectively.
data.problem: The data available on GitHub is often complex and difficult to interpret. To achieve clearer understanding and deeper insights, a more detailed and structured presentation of this data is essential. This was a key need identified by the [EIP Editors](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1#eip-editors) and the [EthCatHerders](https://www.ethcatherders.com/) team. To continue supporting the Ethereum core protocol and application developers, it is crucial to have proposed standards thoroughly reviewed, and the EIP Editors and EthCatHerders team sought data to analyze the resources required for this process.
data.solution: EIPsInsight addresses the challenge of navigating and understanding the complex process of Ethereum Improvement Proposals (EIPs) by providing tools for analyzing pull requests, tracking status changes, and offering visualizations and reports. This helps developers and editors save time, reduce confusion, and make more informed decisions by offering clear insights into the lifecycle and progress of EIPs within the Ethereum ecosystem.
data.missionSummary:
EIPsInsight is dedicated to enhancing Ethereum governance and tooling by providing comprehensive tracking and dynamic visualizations of EIPs, ERCs, and RIPs. Our platform delivers detailed insights into proposal status changes and trends, serving as an indispensable resource for understanding the evolving landscape of Ethereum proposals. With features like customizable downloadable reports, categorized data, and timeline visualizations, EIPsInsight simplifies complex information, empowering editors to make informed decisions.

Aligned with Ethereum's core principles of decentralization, open-source development, and accessibility, EIPsInsight fosters transparency and encourages informed participation. In doing so, it plays a vital role in the sustainability and growth of the Ethereum ecosystem, ensuring that all stakeholders can meaningfully engage in its governance processes.

questions.query: Describe any pioneering development work in your project, particularly in enhancing privacy, interoperability, or user experience.

Recently, we introduced new tools to further enhance the platform. The [EIP Proposal Builder](https://eipsinsight.com/proposalbuilder#split#eip#new) helps users draft new proposals by guiding them through the required format and structure. The Block Countdown Tool, available on the [Pectra page](https://eipsinsight.com/pectra), tracks the number of blocks remaining until the Ethereum network transitions to the Pectra upgrade. questions.query: What specific problems or challenges in the Ethereum ecosystem does your project address? How does your solution improve upon existing alternatives?
questions.explanation:
EIPsInsight addresses inefficiencies in tracking Ethereum Improvement Proposals (EIPs), which were previously managed manually by Ethereum Cat Herders. The lack of automation resulted in delays, outdated records, and limited access to historical data, making governance processes less transparent and efficient.
By automating data collection, EIPsInsight eliminates human error, ensuring real-time tracking of EIP status changes. The platform consolidates historical governance data, enabling users to analyze trends and make informed decisions. Its interactive visualizations, categorized proposal views, and downloadable reports simplify complex governance data, making it more accessible to developers, editors, and the community.
EIPsInsight enhances Ethereum governance by offering dynamic tools like the EIP Board for tracking pull requests, the Proposal Builder for documenting EIPs, and the Network Upgrades Relationships Chart for mapping dependencies. These features ensure a structured, data-driven governance process, aligning with Ethereumâ€™s core values of transparency and decentralizationâ€‹.

questions.query: Outline your project's roadmap and how the grant funds will be used to achieve your development goals.
questions.explanation:
EIPsInsight follows a structured roadmap to improve Ethereum governance tracking. In early 2025, key features like the EIP Board, Proposal Builder, and Target Block Countdown Tool were launched, enhancing proposal management and accessibility.
Q1 2025 focuses on UX audits, accessibility improvements, and tool development, including a Network Upgrades Relationships Chart for tracking EIP dependencies and an EIP Discussion Bot for governance discussions. Q2 2025 will implement UI/UX enhancements, introduce new platform features, and expand the RIPs page with educational content while increasing community engagement through webinars and workshops.
Q3-Q4 2025 aims to introduce AI-powered EIP tracking tools, multi-language support, and customizable smart alerts for real-time governance updates. The funding supports UX improvements, feature enhancements, and community outreach to ensure Ethereumâ€™s governance process remains efficient, decentralized, and accessible.

questions.query: How does your project contribute to the decentralization and security of the Ethereum network?
questions.explanation:
EIPsInsight reinforces decentralization by making Ethereum governance open-source, transparent, and automated. Previously, EIP tracking relied on manual updates, which were prone to errors and inefficiencies. By automating proposal tracking, the platform removes centralized control over governance data, allowing contributors and developers to access reliable information in real-time.
Security is enhanced through improved proposal tracking and verification. The platform ensures that EIPs follow a rigorous approval process, reducing risks associated with unclear or outdated proposals. The historical tracking of governance changes also enables stakeholders to analyze past security challenges, ensuring informed decision-making for future protocol upgrades.
By introducing AI-driven insights and expanding Ethereum governance tracking beyond its ecosystem, EIPsInsight fosters global participation and cross-chain integrations. These innovations make Ethereumâ€™s governance more robust, scalable, and secure, ensuring its long-term sustainabilityâ€‹.
